title: Decent d2 looking for team

embed.description: Summoner Lookup with statistics, ratings, LoLSkillScore and more for TPM Acerino, a League of Legends summoner on the Europe West region.

body:
I was D2 on EuW, can look me up on lolskill/lolnexus - http://www.lolskill.net/summoner/EUW/TPm%20Acerino
I've moved to Australia recently, and since i was a in diamond 4 ranked team for 3's. Enjoyed playing as a team on ts3, I'm decent at any role, mainly adc. Looking for a solid ranked 5's team.  Also for soloq i have 2,5k mmr (high chall)
- Tpm Acerino (in-game name)
